data.description: Welcome to this 3 bed/ 2 bath plus flex space Chiefland Charmer! This charming property is situated in a prime location, offering convenience, comfort, and a sense of community. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious living area provides ample room for relaxation and entertainment, with natural light pouring in through the large windows. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating the perfect space for hosting gatherings or enjoying quality time with family and friends. The kitchen is well-equipped with plenty of countertop and storage space. Whether you're a seasoned chef or just enjoy cooking, this kitchen is sure to meet your needs. The bedrooms are generously sized and offer a peaceful retreat after a long day. With a metal roof that is only 5 years old and a new HVAC along with many additional updates this home is move in ready.   Outside, the property boasts a good size yard, providing a serene escape for outdoor activities or simply enjoying the Florida sunshine. The backyard is a blank canvas, ready for your personal touch and creative landscaping ideas. Located in Chiefland, you'll have easy access to local amenities, schools, shopping centers, and dining options. This property is also conveniently situated near major highways, making commuting a breeze. Don't miss out on this wonderful opportunity to make  this house your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the beauty and comfort this property has to offer. Buyer to verify all school zones and room measurements.
